        <h3>3. Global Exception Handler</h3>
        <p>Create middleware to catch all unhandled exceptions in your request pipeline.</p>

        <div class="my-6 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg bg-[#1e1e1e] ring-1 ring-white/10">
            <div class="flex items-center px-4 py-2 border-b border-white/10 bg-white/5">
